<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM8.10.6">
<l>ēttiyuṉ cēvaṭi yeṇṇi yiruppārai</l>
<l>pārttirun taṅku namaṉṟamar paṟṟātu</l>
<l>cōttamnā mañcutu meṉṟu toṭāmainī</l>
<l>kāttipōl kaṇṇa purattuṟai yammāṉē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>You protect [us], it seems, so that Death’s agents,</l>
<l>Having seen those who honor [you], praising your rosy feet,</l>
<l>Without snatching [at them] then, having said, “Hail! We’re afraid,”</l>
<l>Do not touch [them], lord who dwells in Kaṇṇapuram,</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
